Dear <%= @message.to_employer? ? @application.employer.display_name : @application.job_seeker.display_name %>,

<% if @message.to_employer? %>
  You have received a new message from <%= @application.job_seeker.display_name %> for you current job posting ID# <%= @application.job.id %>, Title "<%= @application.job.title %>".
<% else %>
  You have received a new message from <%= @application.employer.display_name %> for your application for job posting "<%= @application.job.title %>".
<% end %>
<%= @message.content %>

You can view the full conversation in your account using the following link:

<%= application_url(@application) %>
